<div>
    <!DOCTYPE html>
    <html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Document</title>
    </head>
    <style>
        * {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .active {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .active_banner .image {
            padding: 40px 0px;
        }

            .active_banner .image img {
                width: 250px;
                height: 50px;
            }

        .active_body {
            flex: auto;
        }

            .active_body p input {
                border-radius: 15px;
                width: 400px;
                height: 40px;
                border: solid 1px #f6e3e4;
                margin-top: 50px;
                text-indent: 20px;
            }

        .addActive {
            border-radius: 15px;
            width: 400px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: #ff281a;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            margin-top: 70px;
        }

        .active_footer p {
            width: 350px;
            color: #e94230;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 11px;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
    <body>
        <div class="active">
            <div class="active_banner">
                <p class="image">
                    <img class="" src="./image/xsj.jpg" mode="aspectFit|aspectFill|widthFix" lazy-load="false" binderror="" bindload="" />
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="active_body">
                <p>
                    <input class="UserName" placeholder="已注册微信号" />
                </p>
                <p>
                    <button class="addActive" onclick="getInputValue()">查询兑奖号码</button>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <input class="UserName" placeholder="已注册微信号" />
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="active_footer">
                <p>仅限3月19日美商会抽奖活动期间核对中奖信息所用</p>
                <p>请提前加抽奖公布微信号好友以便知晓中奖信息</p>
                <p>过期自动关闭入口</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
    <script>
        function getInputValue() {
            var UserName = document.querySelector('.UserName').value,
                WeChat = document.querySelector('.WeChat').value,
                name = document.querySelector('.name').value;
            alert(`昵称：${UserName},微信号：${WeChat},公司名称：${name}`);
        }
    </script>
</html>
</div>